script.name: plugin.guilds.menu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds'
*skip if $a.event == [MEvent.Update] OR $a.event == [MEvent.IsDisabled] *write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='Guild Board, obj=%s, Event=%s, data=%s', $a.obj, $a.event, $a.data, null, null
$DATA = get global variable: name='guild.menu.data' $guild.data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' $CONFIG = get global variable: name='guilds.config'
if $a.event == [MEvent.IsHidden] if not $a.obj -> is in same sector as [PLAYERSHIP] return [TRUE] else $obj.owner = $a.obj -> get owner race do if $obj.owner == Player return [TRUE] if not $a.obj -> is of class Trading Dock if not $a.obj -> is of class Pirate Dock skip if $a.obj -> get local variable: name='guild.hq' return [TRUE] end end end return [FALSE]
else if $a.event == [MEvent.IsDisabled] if $a.data == 'guild.board' OR $a.data == 'guild.board.ship' $player.docked = [PLAYERSHIP] -> is docked if $player.docked == $a.obj return [FALSE] end if not $CONFIG['guildboard.dock'] if $a.obj ->can player communicate with: check distance=[TRUE] return [FALSE] end end end return [TRUE]
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Switch] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'guild.board' $DATA[$selection] = $value gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Context] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'guild.board' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value2 = $value[0] if $value2 == 'buyware' $target = $value[1] $value = $value[2] $DATA['current.trade.buy'] = $value $ware = $selection gosub sub.BuyWare return $input else if $value2 == 'sellware' $target = $value[1] $value = $value[2] $DATA['current.trade.buy'] = $value $ware = $selection gosub sub.SellWare return $input end else if $value == 'info' if is datatype[ $selection ] == DATATYPE_WARE $input = create input: id='info' encyclopedia page, ware=$selection else $input = create input: id='info' object info page, object=$selection end return $input else if $value == 'escort.accept' $escort.data = $DATA['escorts'] $data = $escort.data[$selection] @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.startescort : Escort=$selection Data=$data remove key $selection from table $escort.data gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu
else if $value == 'bounty.log' $bounties = $guild.data['bounty']['bounties'] if $bounties $bounty.table = $bounties[$selection] if $bounty.table gosub sub.LogBounty return null end end $bounties = $guild.data['assassin']['bounties'] if $bounties $bounty.table = $bounties[$selection] if $bounty.table gosub sub.LogBounty return null end end else if $value == 'passenger.info' $passenger.name = $selection gosub sub.FindPassenger if $passenger.data START $a.obj ->open menu script: script=plugin.guilds.passenger.infomenu, value=$passenger.data return null end else if $value == 'passenger.pickup' $passenger.name = $selection gosub sub.FindPassenger if $passenger.data @ if [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.passenger.board : Ship=[PLAYERSHIP] Passenger Data=$passenger.data gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end end
else if $value == 'bounty.info' $bounties = $guild.data['bounty']['bounties'] if $bounties $bounty.table = $bounties[$selection] if $bounty.table START $a.obj ->open menu script: script=plugin.guilds.bounty.infomenu, value=$bounty.table return null end end $bounties = $guild.data['assassin']['bounties'] if $bounties $bounty.table = $bounties[$selection] if $bounty.table START $a.obj ->open menu script: script=plugin.guilds.bounty.infomenu, value=$bounty.table return null end end else if $value == 'bounty.track' $max.bounties = 3 $bounty.table = $guild.data['tracked.bounty'] if not $bounty.table $bounty.table = table alloc $guild.data['tracked.bounty'] = $bounty.table end $playing.time = playing time $bounty.table[$selection] = $playing.time $size = size of table $bounty.table while $size > $max.bounties $sorted.array = sort table keys by value: table=$bounty.table $value = get first item in array: $sorted.array remove key $value from table $bounty.table $size = size of table $bounty.table end else if $value == 'bounty.untrack' $bounty.table = $guild.data['tracked.bounty'] if $bounty.table $text = $selection -> get local variable: name='bounty.track' do if $text $selection ->set name to $text $selection ->set local variable: name='bounty.track' value=null $selection ->set local variable: name='bounty.track.last' value=null remove key $selection from table $bounty.table end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Hotkey] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'guild.board' if $selection == 'info' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_WARE $input = create input: id='info' encyclopedia page, ware=$value return $input else if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_SHIP $input = create input: id='info' object info page, object=$value return $input end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.HeadingClick] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'guild.board' if $selection == 'bounties' $tmp = $DATA['bounty.sort'] if $value <= 190 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'name' else if $value <= 370 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'ship' else if $value <= 520 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'sector' else if $value <= 580 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'id' else if $value <= 660 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'race' else if $value <= 720 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'type' else if $value <= 770 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'xp' else $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'pay' end $tmp2 = $DATA['bounty.sort'] if $tmp2 == $tmp if $DATA['bounty.sortorder'] $DATA['bounty.sortorder'] = [FALSE] else $DATA['bounty.sortorder'] = [TRUE] end else $DATA['bounty.sortorder'] = [FALSE] end
else if $selection == 'escort.tab' $tmp = $DATA['escort.sort'] if $value <= 260 $DATA['escort.sort'] = 'name' else if $value <= 360 $DATA['escort.sort'] = 'race' else if $value <= 610 $DATA['escort.sort'] = 'dest' else if $value <= 675 $DATA['escort.sort'] = 'level' else if $value <= 725 $DATA['escort.sort'] = 'jumps' else $DATA['escort.sort'] = 'price' end $tmp2 = $DATA['escort.sort'] if $tmp2 == $tmp if $DATA['escort.sortorder'] $DATA['escort.sortorder'] = [FALSE] else $DATA['escort.sortorder'] = [TRUE] end else $DATA['escort.sortorder'] = [FALSE] end
else if $selection == 'passengers' $tmp = $DATA['passenger.sort'] if $value <= 200 $DATA['passenger.sort'] = 'name' else if $value <= 350 $DATA['passenger.sort'] = 'sector' else if $value <= 450 $DATA['passenger.sort'] = 'type' else if $value <= 550 $DATA['passenger.sort'] = 'travel.type' else if $value <= 700 $DATA['passenger.sort'] = 'destination' else $DATA['passenger.sort'] = 'pay' end $tmp2 = $DATA['passenger.sort'] if $tmp2 == $tmp if $DATA['passenger.sortorder'] $DATA['passenger.sortorder'] = [FALSE] else $DATA['passenger.sortorder'] = [TRUE] end else $DATA['passenger.sortorder'] = [FALSE] end else if $selection == 'trade.buy' $tmp = $DATA['trade.sort'] if $value <= 200 $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'name' else if $value <= 240 $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'vol' else if $value <= 270 $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'tc' else if $value <= 320 $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'qty' else if $value <= 450 $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'guild' else if $value <= 530 $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'per' else if $value <= 630 $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'total' else $DATA['trade.sort'] = 'expire' end $tmp2 = $DATA['trade.sort'] if $tmp2 == $tmp if $DATA['trade.sortorder'] $DATA['trade.sortorder'] = [FALSE] else $DATA['trade.sortorder'] = [TRUE] end else $DATA['trade.sortorder'] = [FALSE] end end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.TradeBarCh] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'buy.ware' $value.id = $DATA['current.trade.buy'] $ware = $guild.data['ware.buying'][$value.id] $ware = $ware[0] $target = $selection $current = $value gosub sub.BuyWare return $menu else if $menu.id == 'sell.ware' $value.id = $DATA['current.trade.buy'] $ware = $guild.data['ware.selling'][$value.id] $ware = $ware[0] $target = $selection $current = $value gosub sub.SellWare return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Update] $menu.id = $a.data[0] if $menu.id == 'guild.board' gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Select] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] if $menu.id == 'guild.board' if $guild.data[$selection] START $a.obj ->open menu script: script=plugin.guilds.infomenu, value=$selection end else if $menu.id == 'buy.ware' $value = $DATA['current.trade.buy'] $trade.data = $guild.data['ware.buying'][$value] $value = $a.data[3] $price = $trade.data[2] $price = $price * $value $money = get player money if $price > $money START speak text: page=[Page.MiscVoice] id=1254 priority=80 else $value = $DATA['current.trade.buy'] $value.qty = $a.data[3] @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.usetrade : Trade ID=$value Buying?=[TRUE] Qty=$value.qty Destination=$selection $value = $trade.data[0] $voice = get text id: ware=$value $voice = create new array, arguments=[Page.ObjDesc], $voice, [Page.MiscVoice], 1273, null START speak array: $voice prio=80 return [TRUE] end else if $menu.id == 'sell.ware' $value = $DATA['current.trade.buy'] $trade.data = $guild.data['ware.selling'][$value] $value.qty = $a.data[3] @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.usetrade : Trade ID=$value Buying?=[FALSE] Qty=$value.qty Destination=$selection $value = $trade.data[0] $voice = get text id: ware=$value $voice = create new array, arguments=[Page.ObjDesc], $voice, [Page.MiscVoice], 1272, null START speak array: $voice prio=80 return [TRUE] end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.TabChanged] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] if $menu.id == 'guild.board' $DATA['tab'] = $selection gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] $DATA = table alloc $DATA['tab'] = 0 $DATA['bounty.sort'] = 'name' $DATA['passenger.sort'] = 'name' $DATA['guild.filter.bounty'] = 0 gosub sub.BuildMenu set global variable: name='guild.menu.data' value=$DATA return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished] set global variable: name='guild.menu.data' value=null end
return null
sub.LogBounty: if $bounty.table $v1 = $bounty.table['pilot'] $v2 = $bounty.table['ship'] $v3 = $v2 -> get ID code $v2 = $v2 -> get name $v4 = $bounty.table['sector'] $v5 = $bounty.table['pay'] $v5 = convert number $v5 to string write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Personal], pageid=$page.id textid=1136, $v1, $v2, $v3, $v4, $v5 end endsub
sub.BuildMenu: $current.tab = $DATA['tab'] $menu = create custom menu array
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=101 add tab to menu: $menu, text=$read.text do if $current.tab == 0 gosub sub.BountyTab
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=102 add tab to menu: $menu, text=$read.text do if $current.tab == 1 gosub sub.PassengerTab
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=103 add tab to menu: $menu, text=$read.text do if $current.tab == 2 gosub sub.EscortTab
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=104 add tab to menu: $menu, text=$read.text do if $current.tab == 3 gosub sub.TradeTab
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=105 add tab to menu: $menu, text=$read.text do if $current.tab == 4 gosub sub.TaskTab
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=106 add tab to menu: $menu, text=$read.text do if $current.tab == 5 gosub sub.InfoTab
set menu option: $menu, icon=4 set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Huge] set menu option: $menu, remove main header=[TRUE]
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100 $callback = [Callback.TabChanged] | [Callback.Switch] $input = create input: id='guild.board', dynamic menu=$menu, title=$read.text, description=$a.obj, callback=$callback, update=2000ms endsub
* ============================================= * ============================================= sub.BountyTab:
$aGuilds = create new array, arguments='bounty', 'assassin', null, null, null
$size = size of array $aGuilds $aValues = array alloc: size=$size $i = 0 while $i < $size $guild.name = $aGuilds[$i] $tGuild = $guild.data[$guild.name] $text.id = $tGuild['name'] $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text.id $aValues[$i] = $read.text inc $i = end
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=115 insert $read.text into array $aValues at index 0 $default = $DATA['guild.filter.bounty'] $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=116 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id='guild.filter.bounty', width=160 allowtabs=[TRUE]
$section = 0 while $section < 2 $sort.value = $DATA['bounty.sort'] $added = 0 inc $section =
$text.cols = array alloc: size=8 if $section == 1 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1019 else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1000 end $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=150 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[7] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1013 $text = create custom menu column string, position=190 length=150 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1001 $text = create custom menu column string, position=370 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1002 $text = create custom menu column string, position=520 length=80 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1003 $text = create custom menu column string, position=580 length=80 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1004 $text = create custom menu column string, position=660 length=80 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[4] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1009 $text = create custom menu column string, position=720 length=50 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[5] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1005 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[6] = $text add clickable heading: menu=$menu, text=$text.cols, id='bounties', allow empty=[TRUE]
* find all valid bounties $table = table alloc
if $section == 1 $bounty.table = $guild.data['tracked.bounty'] if $bounty.table $key = get next key: table=$bounty.table key=null while $key $i = 0 $size = size of array $aGuilds while $i < $size $guild.name = $aGuilds[$i] $bounties = $guild.data[$guild.name]['bounties'] if $bounties $tmp = $bounties[$key] do if $tmp $table[$key] = $tmp end inc $i = end $key = get next key: table=$bounty.table key=$key end end else $default = $DATA['guild.filter.bounty'] if $default dec $default = $guild.name = $aGuilds[$default] gosub sub.AddBounties else $size = size of array $aGuilds $i = 0 while $i < $size $guild.name = $aGuilds[$i] gosub sub.AddBounties inc $i = end end end
$table.data = table alloc $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key if $sort.value == 'name' $sort.text = $key -> get pilot name else if $sort.value == 'ship' $sort.text = $key -> get local variable: name='bounty.track' skip if $sort.text $sort.text = $key -> get name else if $sort.value == 'sector' $sort.text = $table[$key]['sector'] else if $sort.value == 'id' $sort.text = $key -> get ID code else if $sort.value == 'race' $sort.text = $table[$key]['race'] else if $sort.value == 'type' $sort.text = $table[$key]['type'] else if $sort.value == 'pay' $sort.text = $table[$key]['pay'] else if $sort.value $sort.text = $table[$key][$sort.value] skip if $sort.text $sort.text = $key -> get name else $sort.text = $key -> get name end $table.data[$key] = $sort.text $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key end
$sorted.array = sort table keys by value: table=$table.data
do if $DATA['bounty.sortorder'] $sorted.array = reverse array $sorted.array
$size = size of array $sorted.array $i = 0 while $i < $size $key = $sorted.array[$i] $table.data = $table[$key] inc $i = $text.cols = array alloc: size=10 $text = $table.data['type'] if $text == 3 $text = create custom menu string icon: type=[IconType.Gui], id=92, Y=1 Width=8 Height=10 else $text = create custom menu string icon: type=[IconType.Gui], id=90, Y=1 Width=8 Height=10 end $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=8 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $text = $key -> get pilot name $text = create custom menu column string, position=10 length=180 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text $text = $key ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=190 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[8] = $text $text = $key -> get local variable: name='bounty.track' skip if $text $text = $key -> get name $text = create custom menu column string, position=200 length=170 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[9] = $text
$text = $table.data['sector'] $text = create custom menu column string, position=370 length=150 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text $text = $key -> get ID code $text = create custom menu column string, position=520 length=60 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[3] = $text $text = $table.data['race'] $text = create custom menu column string, position=580 length=80 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[4] = $text $text = $table.data['type'] if $text == 2 $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1011 else if $text == 3 $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1012 else if $text == 4 $text = read text: page=$page.id id=400000 else $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1010 end $text = create custom menu column string, position=660 length=70 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[5] = $text $text = $table.data['xp'] $text = convert number $text to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=730 length=45 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[6] = $text $text = $table.data['pay'] $text = convert number $text to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text, [Text.Credits], null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[7] = $text
$context = create context menu $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=812 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=29, returnvalue='bounty.info', hotkey=[Key.Identity], disabled=[FALSE] add context menu separator: menu=$context
if $guild.data['tracked.bounty'][$key] $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1023 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=59, returnvalue='bounty.untrack', hotkey=[Key.Target], disabled=[FALSE] else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1022 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=59, returnvalue='bounty.track', hotkey=[Key.Target], disabled=[FALSE] end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1025 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=33, returnvalue='bounty.log', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE]
$text = $key -> get pilot name $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1024 add context menu global info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$text $text = $table.data['guild'] if $text $text = $guild.data[$text]['name'] $text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=117 add context menu global info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$text end
$ret = create menu return value: context menu, id=$key, menu=$context, dynamic=[FALSE] add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.cols returnvalue=$ret inc $added = end
if $added <= 0 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text end end endsub
* ============================================= * ============================================= sub.AddBounties: $tData = $guild.data[$guild.name] if $tData $guild.hq = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='guild.owner' if $guild.hq != $guild.name $guild.hq = null end if $tData['member'] $guild.level = $tData['level'] $tmp = $tData['bounties'] if $tmp $max.range = $CONFIG['bounty.range'] $obj.sector = $a.obj -> get sector $key = get next key: table=$tmp key=null while $key $value = $tmp[$key] $level = $value['level'] if $guild.level >= $level $sector = $value['sector'] $jumps = get jumps from sector $sector to sector $obj.sector if $jumps <= $max.range if $guild.hq $table[$key] = $value else $obj.owner = $a.obj -> get owner race $bounty.owner = $value['gov'] do if $bounty.owner == $obj.owner $table[$key] = $value end end end $key = get next key: table=$tmp key=$key end end end end endsub
* ============================================= * ============================================= sub.PassengerTab: $default = $DATA['guild.filter.taxi'] skip if $default $default = 0
$aValues = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102302 $aValues[0] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102301 $aValues[1] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100031 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$aValues, default=$default, return id='guild.filter.taxi', width=160 allowtabs=[TRUE]
$text.cols = array alloc: size=6 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100010 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100011 $text = create custom menu column string, position=200 length=150 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100012 $text = create custom menu column string, position=350 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100013 $text = create custom menu column string, position=450 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100014 $text = create custom menu column string, position=550 length=150 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[4] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100015 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[5] = $text
add clickable heading: menu=$menu, text=$text.cols, id='passengers', allow empty=[FALSE]
$tGuild = $guild.data['taxi'] $tPassengers = $tGuild['passengers'] $tDisplayPassengers = table alloc
if $tGuild['member'] if $tPassengers $max.jumps = $CONFIG['passenger.board.range'] skip if $max.jumps $max.jumps = 0
$obj.sector = $a.obj -> get sector $key = get next key: table=$tPassengers key=null while $key $table = $tPassengers[$key] $passenger.name = get next key: table=$table key=null while $passenger.name $sector = $table[$passenger.name]['sector'] if $DATA['guild.filter.taxi'] if $sector == $obj.sector $tDisplayPassengers[$passenger.name] = $table[$passenger.name] end else $jumps = get jumps from sector $sector to sector $obj.sector do if $jumps <= $max.jumps $tDisplayPassengers[$passenger.name] = $table[$passenger.name] end $passenger.name = get next key: table=$table key=$passenger.name end
$key = get next key: table=$tPassengers key=$key end end end
if not $tDisplayPassengers $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else if not size of table $tDisplayPassengers $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else $table.data = table alloc $sort.value = $DATA['passenger.sort'] $passenger.name = get next key: table=$tDisplayPassengers key=null while $passenger.name $passenger.data = $tDisplayPassengers[$passenger.name] $sort.text = $passenger.data[$sort.value] if $sort.value == 'travel.type' $sort.text = $passenger.data['travel.type'] $sort.text = $sort.text + 100020 $sort.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$sort.text else if $sort.value == 'destination' gosub sub.PassengerDestination $sort.text = $read.text end if not $sort.text $sort.text = $passenger.data['name'] end $table.data[$passenger.name] = $sort.text $passenger.name = get next key: table=$tDisplayPassengers key=$passenger.name end
$sorted.array = sort table keys by value: table=$table.data do if $DATA['passenger.sortorder'] $sorted.array = reverse array $sorted.array
